10:45.150 --> 10:46.740
Jason ended up serving god.

10:46.800 --> 10:48.020
I'm a corporate lawyer.

10:48.080 --> 10:49.270
Then solve it from the inside.

10:49.330 --> 10:50.490
Once you get the corner office,

10:50.570 --> 10:54.070
nobody from that firm's ever gonna ask 
