Are you sure about this?

14:02.390 --> 14:03.810
Yeah,I think so.

14:05.020 --> 14:07.370
Just...going there every day,

14:07.430 --> 14:11.080
supporting people and denying myself,I--

14:11.140 --> 14:13.440
and then the life that I lived before I...

14:14.570 --> 14:16.410
before you came out?

